descriptions.value: The Glock 18 is a serviceable first-round pistol that works best against unarmored opponents and is capable of firing three-round bursts. Menacing bullets and a War Maiden in a pink jacket have been custom painted over a yellow and black base. "I'll stop shooting when you start shushing"
Sticker: Nemiga | 2020 RMR
This item features StatTrak™ technology, which tracks certain statistics when equipped by its owner.

More accurate but less damaging than its AK-47 counterpart, the M4A4 is the full-auto assault rifle of choice for CTs. It has been custom painted with a stylized blue-magenta woman over a grayscale background. "She grabbed what she could and disappeared into a decaying dystopia"

The Storage Unit allows you to store up to 1,000 of your surplus items which would otherwise exceed inventory limit. At any time you can move items from your inventory into the Storage Unit, retrieve items back into your inventory, or you can just use it to organize your collectibles.

A low-recoil firearm with a high rate of fire, the P250 is a relatively inexpensive choice against armored opponents. It has been custom painted with a silver slide and hexagon-textured grip. You represent the front line of our cyber security effort

Historically a focal point of contention and even regulation, this Italian-style stiletto switchblade knife features a spring-loaded blade that can be deployed almost instantly with the push of a release catch. It is still perfectly operational although the exterior surfaces have rusted. Some people don't need to hide how dirty their deeds are
This graffiti can be applied to the in-game world. You can apply it until you run out of charges.

A less expensive option among the terrorist-exclusive assault rifles, the Galil AR is a serviceable weapon in medium to long-range combat. A hydrographic pattern of red hexagons has been applied over a dark blue base. Information is never free

A fan favorite from Counter-Strike Source, the Silenced USP Pistol has a detachable silencer that gives shots less recoil while suppressing attention-getting noise. It has been given discreet red highlights to give off a futuristic feel. Imogen was the past Felix, I'm the future - Huxley, The Competition

High risk and high reward, the infamous AWP is recognizable by its signature report and one-shot, one-kill policy. It has been custom painted using the Death tarot card as inspiration. Every end is a new beginning
This item commemorates the 2022 PGL Antwerp CS:GO Championship.

This is a commemorative PGL 2022 Antwerp CS:GO Major Championship Coin which tracks your progress throughout the event, provides full access to the Antwerp 2022 Pick'Em Challenge, Steam.tv chat flairs, coin challenges, and unlimited graffiti opportunities in-game for the duration of the event.

Upgrade your Antwerp 2022 Coin by completing coin challenges. Earn a Souvenir Token every time you upgrade your coin.
This item features StatTrak™ technology, which tracks certain statistics when equipped by its owner.
*Stats for this item will reset when used in Steam Trading or Community Market

A cheap option for cash-strapped players, the FAMAS effectively fills the niche between more expensive rifles and the less-effective SMGs. It's stark white and black design make it feel like it came from a sci-fi show. Spikey blue hair and robot companion not included
Sticker: Kawaii Killer Terrorist, Little Mischief

A low-recoil firearm with a high rate of fire, the P250 is a relatively inexpensive choice against armored opponents. It has been custom painted with a sci-fi design. If you think I need a rifle to kill a man, you have no idea who you're talking to... - Mikha Biton, Phoenix Sniper

Powerful and reliable, the AK-47 is one of the most popular assault rifles in the world. It is most deadly in short, controlled bursts of fire. It has been custom painted using the Empress tarot card as inspiration. Wealth comes in many forms
Sticker: Fast Banana, Run CT, Run, Sneaky Beaky Dept. (Holo), Drug War Veteran

Manufactured in Switzerland, the cutting-edge MP9 SMG is an ergonomic polymer weapon favored by private security firms. This brightly colored MP9 has been custom painted with a monster food chain. Eat or be eaten

The misunderstood middle child of the SMG family, the UMP45's small magazine is the only drawback to an otherwise versatile close-quarters automatic. It has been given a decal of a sabertooth tiger skull Every predator eventually meets their end

Essentially a box that bullets come out of, the MAC-10 SMG boasts a high rate of fire, with poor spread accuracy and high recoil as trade-offs. It has been custom painted using a pearlescent finish to resemble holographic self-adhesive vinyl. Depending on the light its appearance changes. Watch when you point that thing

As expensive as it is powerful, the Desert Eagle is an iconic pistol that is difficult to master but surprisingly accurate at long range. A pink isometric pattern has been custom painted on the barrel. The hammer and front sight have been painted bright blue. Patience is its own reward

The Storage Unit allows you to store up to 1,000 of your surplus items which would otherwise exceed inventory limit. At any time you can move items from your inventory into the Storage Unit, retrieve items back into your inventory, or you can just use it to organize your collectibles.

The Glock 18 is a serviceable first-round pistol that works best against unarmored opponents and is capable of firing three-round bursts. The steel slide has been painted using a combination of stenciling and hand-painting using oil paints. The only way to make diamonds is by applying pressure
